data.description: Gorgeous Pool home on a corner lot, this property comes with tons of improvements, including a new roof in 2023, a new AC unit, a new kitchen, a new floor, impact windows, and a camera's system. Its key ready to move in. The main house has been converted into four bedrooms and two bathrooms, and it has two more additions, generating $ 2200 on a monthly basis. Located less than 15 minutes away from Sunny Isles and Hallandale beaches, Aventura Mall It's conveniently located next to the 826, supermarkets, shopping centers, and gas stations. Do not miss this one-of-a-kind opportunity. Give me a call for more details. Equal Housing Opportunity.
